  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataManager
    A base interface for a class acting as a data manager for arbitrary types of objects.
    DataManagerApiTests
    Created by rishi on 15-10-30.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseDataManagerTests<T extends DataManager>
    Created by rishi on 15-10-30.
    CachedDataManager
    A JsonDataManager that wraps around an inner JsonDataManager to keep a copy of the data in a local cache using an LocalDataManager.
    CachedDataManagerTests
    Created by rishi on 15-10-31.
    DataKey
    A class that acts as the key mapping to an object being stored by a DataManager.
    DataKeyNotFoundException
    Subclass of NotFoundException thrown when a particular DataKey is not found by a DataManager.
    HttpDataManager
    A JsonDataManager that uses the ElasticSearch server as the storage media.
    HttpDataManagerTests
    Created by rishi on 15-10-30.
    JsonDataManager
    An abstract implementation of DataManager that stores the objects as JSONs to a storage media.
    JsonDataManagerTests
    Created by rishi on 15-10-29.
    JsonFormatter
    A class for specifying the JSON format the JsonDataManager should use.
    LocalDataManager
    A JsonDataManager that stores the serialized JSONs locally in the phone's storage.
    LocalDataManagerTests
    Created by rishi on 15-10-30.
    QueuedDataManager
    A CachedDataManager that uses JobManager for queuing up the the write and deletion operations.
    QueuedDataManagerTests
    Created by rishi on 15-11-11.
